    <descript>
      <abstract>Measurements of full-spectrum (i.e. 350-2500nm) canopy spectral reflectance of Arctic plant species.  Spectra were collected using the HR-2014i together with a Spectralon white plate to calibrate each measurement under variable illumination conditions. Additional details can be found in the resulting publications</abstract>
